Villaggio Rustico White Loaf Bread
description: "Inspired by traditional recipes, Villaggio Rustico White Loaf is a white bread with rich and hearty flavour. Fresh from the hearth oven, it has a soft, yet sturdy texture with slight chewiness that makes it's a pleasure to bite into. Toast it with your favourite spread, create satisfying sandwiches for lunch or dinner, or enjoy it buttered as a side with soups and chilis. This bread is a great addition to your table, whether you are hosting a gathering or simply enjoying a meal with your family at home."

name: Vachon Ah Caramel The Original Cakes
description: "Bite into pure bliss with Vachon Ah Caramel! The Original Cakes. Overflowing with caramel and creamy filling and coated with a chocolatey layer, this soft and spongy cake delivers a decadent flavour experience. Enjoy straight out of the box or freeze for a cool and crunchy sweet indulgence. Twin wrapped, they're great for sharing or doubling up on the go. Made in Sainte-Marie-de-Beauce in Quebec, Vachon snack cakes have brought joy to families since 1923."

name: Vachon Swiss Rolls Original Cakes
description: Vachon Swiss Rolls Original Cakes roll up a decadent blend of chocolatey goodness and sweet creamy filling into one delicious snack. These cake snacks are prepared in Quebec with no artificial colours or flavours and come conveniently twin-wrapped for easy sharing and snacking.

name: Vachon Ah Louis Caramel/Red Velvet Cakes
description: "Prepared in Quebec with a fusion of your favourite Vachon textures and flavours, Vachon Ah Louis Caramel/Red Velvet Cakes are the ultimate treats. Combining lush Jos Louis red velvet cake and chocolatey coating with decadent Ah Caramel! creamy filling, this easy-to-enjoy snack is a truly tasty indulgence. Each package contains two Ah Louis cakes for convenient sharing”not that we'd blame you if you kept them all for yourself. Add them to lunchboxes for a sweet midday reward or savour them with coffee or tea as an easy after-dinner dessert. There's no wrong time to enjoy this decadent snack. Crafting delicious treats since 1923, Vachon is known for snacks with the quality and taste families have loved for decades."

name: Vachon Jos Louis The Original Cakes
description: Vachon The Original Jos Louis Cakes deliver an irresistible combination of sponge cake and creamy filling coated in a delicious chocolatey layer.

name: Farmer's Market Butter Croissant
description: The Farmer's Market brand is your assurance that we have searched far and near to offer you and your family great-tasting quality products and value you can count on.

name: Vachon Flaky Pastries Three Fruits

name: Hostess Twinkies Cakes
description: "Hostess Twinkies Cakes creamy, fluffy, golden cakes filled with an irresistible creamy filling. A favourite snack with kids and adults alike."

name: Vachon Flaky Pastries Apple-Raspberry
description: Vachon Passion Flakie Apple-Raspberry Flaky Pastries are filled with delicious fruity and creamy filling for a light-tasting and luscious snack.

name: Farmer's Market Lemon Poppyseed Iced Loaf Cake
description: "Serve Lemon Poppyseed Iced Loaf Cake at family dinners for dessert with a warm cup of coffee, tea, or hot chocolate. The loaf cake is moist, speckled with yummy poppy seeds, and iced to perfection."

Country Harvest Cinnamon Raisin Bread
description: "Everything We Bake Is Whole Grain And Begins At The Harvest, With Flavourful Yet Nourishing Ingredients. Country Harvest Raisin Cinnamon Bread Is Made With Whole Grains, And Is Perfectly Spiced And Baked With Cinnamon And Sweet Raisins. Pre-Sliced With No Artificial Colours Or Flavours And No Trans Fat."

name: Farmer's Market Oatmeal Raisin Cookies
description: Wholesome Cookies Made With The Goodness Of Oatmeal And Sweet Raisins.

name: President's Choice Flake Outs Churro Croissant Donuts
description: "What looks like a donut on the outside, looks like a croissant on the inside and tastes like a twist on a cinnamon delight? If you didn't guess PC Churro Flake Outs Croissant Donuts, don't feel bad, because they're something completely unmistakable and truly craveable! Bite into its donut-y exterior and you'll find it's truly a croissant at heart with all the rich, airy flakiness you'd come to expect (24 layers of it, to be precise). And the icing on top: a bakery-worthy caramel flavoured glaze, crowned with crunchy cinnamon cookie pieces."

ACE Demi Baguette BYO
description: "Our ACE Bakery bread is made using our aged starters, simple ingredients and traditional techniques, but it's anything but ordinary. Take this ACE Bakery Demi-Baguette - traditional white baguette with a creamy inside, fully developed flavour and perfectly crisp golden crust.Simply warm it up, eat and enjoy!Baking Instructions: The loaf you are about to enjoy has been partially baked at ACE Bakery. Do not defrost before baking.Remove from packaging. Place frozen loaf on a bakingtray in a 410Ā°F (200Ā°C) oven for 8-10 minutes. To finishthe baking process, remove from oven and let rest for 10minutes before eating.Visit us at ACEBakery.com for more recipe inspiration."

name: Anmol Fruitcake
description: "Fruitcake is a traditional holiday cake made with candied fruit, nuts, spices, and liquor. It typically has a very long shelf life and is a popular gift during the Christmas season."

name: ACE Ciabatta Pezzetti Duo
description: "Our ACE Bakery bread is made using our aged starters, simple ingredients and traditional techniques, but it's anything but ordinary.ACE Bakery Ciabatta Pezzetti Duo rolls are exceptionally light with a moist, airy interior.
